how to install streamlit on windows:
1. Install python using these command:
1.1 Access to web browser
1.2 Goto python download page : https://www.python.org/downloads/windows/
1.3 Click appropriate download link for your system (32 bits or 64 bits)
1.4 Follow the instruction for installation
1.5 In optional features, tick pip (or tick all option)
1.6 In advance options, tick Add python to environment variables
1.7 if complete installation check with command prompt
1.8 Open command prompt (Press window key + r
1.9 In command prompt
    C:\Users\[User Name]>pip --version

1.10 if shows version, then the installation is completed

2. Install streamlit
2.1 Use in command propmt
  C:\Users\[User Name]>pip install streamlit
2.2 After completed, continue in command prompt
  C:\Users\[User Name]>streamlit hello
     Welcome to Streamlit
